data.name: lblAStam.Text
data.value:
Attacking requires 10 stamina, if you do not have 10 stamina, you are not able to attack. You regenerate 5 stamina at the end of each turn, regardless of whether you attacked or blocked. Blocking reduces damage received by 50% and regenerates and additional 20 stamina.
The player and the enemy have a chance to dodge incoming attacks, player dodge chance is 20% by default, then modified the the evasion stat on Weapons and Armor.
There are two types of damage: Normal Damage and Armor Piercing (AP) Damage. Normal damage is reduced by the target's defense stat. a flat percentage of damage reduced. AP Damage ignores all armor and is applied directly.
